MAMBA-Frost API_PKC Directory

This directory is the official API_PKC adaptation directory for MAMBA-Frost.
MAMBA-Frost is an LWQ-Z KEM.
Frost was previously developed under the working name Venom.

Directory layout
- Implementations/
  - Reference_Implementation/: ISO C reference implementations.
  - Optimized_Implementation/: optimized implementations for 64-bit PC platforms.
  - Additional_Implementation/: additional or platform-specific implementations.
- Test_Vectors/: packaging location for generated API_PKC KAT vectors.

Official parameter-set instances
- MAMBA-Frost-128
- MAMBA-Frost-192
- MAMBA-Frost-256
- MAMBA-Frost-384
- MAMBA-Frost-512
